♬ In and around the lake

3579
04:09:09,532 --> 04:09:13,532
♬ Mountains come out of
the sky and they stand there

3580
04:09:16,706 --> 04:09:20,306
♬ One mile over we'll be there
and we'll see you

3581
04:09:23,046 --> 04:09:24,547
♬ Ten true summers

3582
04:09:24,547 --> 04:09:26,847
♬ we'll be there
