3583
04:09:29,419 --> 04:09:32,288
♬ Twenty four before
my love you'll see

3584
04:09:32,288 --> 04:09:38,194
♬ I'll be there with you

3585
04:09:38,194 --> 04:09:57,347
♬～

3586
04:09:57,347 --> 04:09:59,182
♬ Along the drifting cloud,

3587
